headline: Karat Launches Partner Talent Solution to Elevate Contractor Engineering Quality
summary: SEATTLE, August 21, 2025--Karat, the trusted standard for measuring technical talent, today announced the launch of the industry’s first-ever solution for elevating contractor engineering quality.
